 declared.","summary":"GCPL's Q3 net profit fell marginally to Rs 498 cr; sales rose 9% YoY to Rs 4,079.5 cr.\nIndia sales grew 11%, Indonesia revenue fell 2.8%, and Africa surged 19.4%; Rs 5/share interim dividend declared.","url":"https://www.news18.com/agency-feeds/gcpl-net-profit-falls-marginally-to-rs-498-cr-in-q3-sales-rise-9-pc-9852409.html","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-01-23T19:15:00","source":"News18"},{"id":"802486026680870528","title":"Godrej Consumer Products reports 9% YoY consolidated revenue growth; standalone organic sales grew 11%.\nRegional sales mixed: Indonesia down 3%, Africa/USA/Middle East up 19%; net profit up 14% excluding one-offs.","summary":"Godrej Consumer Products reports 9% YoY consolidated revenue growth; standalone organic sales grew 11%.\nRegional sales mixed: Indonesia down 3%, Africa/USA/Middle East up 19%; net profit up 14% excluding one-offs.","url":"https://sqst.in/gT59a","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-01-23T16:02:58","source":"ScoutQuest"},{"id":"451942","title":"Godrej Consumer Products Ltd approved unaudited Q3 FY26 results, showing consolidated revenue of ₹4,079.47 crore and PAT of ₹497.91 crore.\nThe board declared an interim dividend of ₹5/share, with record date January 30, 2026, and payment by February 22, 2026.","summary":"Godrej Consumer Products Ltd approved unaudited Q3 FY26 results, showing consolidated revenue of ₹4,079.47 crore and PAT of ₹497.91 crore.\nThe board declared an interim dividend of ₹5/share, with record date January 30, 2026, and payment by February 22, 2026.","url":"https://www.bseindia.com/stockinfo/AnnPdfOpen.aspx?Pname=b59ba499-a7d2-4316-bce9-8a5354aeb37f.pdf","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-01-23T15:43:46","source":"BSE"}]}]